OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772291020
OL,3,CTwo held on suspected murder plot re-
OL,4,Carrested under terrorism laws
OL,6,FA man and woman detained in Hull have
OL,7,Fbeen re-arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fpreparing terrorist acts.
OL,10,FThe 23-year-olds were arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to murder on
OL,12,FThursday following an investigation by
OL,13,Fcounter-terrorism police.
OL,15,FA house in the city was also searched
OL,16,Fin connection.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
