PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772291020
OL,3,CTwo held on suspected murder plot re-
OL,4,Carrested under terrorism laws
OL,6,FCounter Terrorism Policing North East
OL,7,F(CTPNE), which has been leading the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said on Friday it had
OL,9,Fre-arrested the two and had been
OL,10,Fgranted permission to hold them for up
OL,11,Fto seven days.
OL,13,FPolice can hold suspects for up to 14
OL,14,Fdays under the Terrorism Act in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales.
OL,17,FThe CTPNE did not reveal any further
OL,18,Fdetails surrounding the suspected
OL,19,Fterrorism preparations, only that they
OL,20,Fhad initially been questioned on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772291020
OL,3,CTwo held on suspected murder plot re-
OL,4,Carrested under terrorism laws
OL,6,FThe man, described as white British,
OL,7,Fwas also originally arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of possessing an offensive
OL,9,Fweapon.
OL,11,FThe woman's ethnicity meanwhile was
OL,12,Flisted as white Polish.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the unit said:
OL,15,F"They have both been rearrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of the preparation of
OL,17,Fterrorist acts, contrary to Section 5
OL,18,Fof the Terrorism Act 2006.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
