OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772291020
OL,3,CTwo held on suspected murder plot re-
OL,4,Carrested under terrorism laws
OL,6,F"Both currently remain in custody. A
OL,7,FWarrant of Further Detention was
OL,8,Fgranted today (Friday, February 27)
OL,9,Ffor seven days, giving officers until
OL,10,FThursday, March 5, to hold the
OL,11,Fsuspects."
OL,13,FSearches at the house in Hull remained
OL,14,Fongoing on Friday.
OL,16,FThe force said the arrests had been
OL,17,Fpre-planned and based on intelligence,
OL,18,Fadding there was not believed to be
OL,19,Fany immediate risk to the community.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
